  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK968">
<l>maruntōmaṟ ṟūṉōmpum vāḻkkai peruntakaimai</l>
<l>pīṭaḻiya vanta viṭattu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For the high-born to keep their body in life when their honour is gone will certainly not prove a remedy against death.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
